== Egg Bites ==

MICROWAVE: Open plastic packaging slightly to vent. With egg bite in packaging, microwave until heated through, ~{40-60%seconds}.

TOASTER OVEN: Preheat #toaster oven{} to 350 degrees. Remove egg bite from plastic packaging and place in toaster oven. Cook until heated through, ~{5-10%minutes}.

== Muffin ==

Enjoy your @Blueberry Muffin{2} and @Chocolate Chip Muffin{2}!

== Belgian Waffle ==

Heat a #waffle iron{}. Add @Belgian Waffle{2} to iron. Warm for about ~{30%seconds}.

TOASTER OR OVEN: Heat #toaster{} or traditional #oven{} to low. Add waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about ~{1%minute}.

MICROWAVE: Microwave waffle for ~{20%seconds}.

== Latte ==

Serve @La Colombe Vanilla Oat Lattes{3} and @La Colombe Triple Lattes{4} over ice and enjoy!

> Not a morning person? We hear you! Luckily, we've cracked the code to making your morning a little easier (and significantly more delicious). Enter this bundle of vegetarian faves: Hearty red pepper and cheese plus spinach and feta sous-vide egg bites are super-easy to prepare, just heat and eat! You'll also get blueberry and chocolate chip muffins with pillowy tops and a moist crumb (no baking required!) Belgian waffles warm up in the microwave or toaster—a decadent treat in a flash. And we didn't forget your caffeine fix: two types of creamy, ready-to-drink lattes: a low-sugar oat milk variety and a milky triple-shot—all you have to do is crack open a can!